---
// Hero — homepage opener. Stance follows v2: italic serif, single
// line break, "usability amplifier" emphasised in amber. The role
// eyebrow + Alt+T hint live in SiteHeader now (rendered once, at
// every breakpoint) rather than duplicated here. Stats live in
// HeroStats.astro, directly after this section.
---

<section class="hero container" aria-label="Introduction">
  <p class="hero__stance">
    Accessibility isn't a feature. <br />
    It's a <em class="hero__emphasis">usability amplifier</em>.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-block: 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero__stance {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

.hero__emphasis {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--amber-11);
  }

  html.dark .hero__emphasis {
    color: var(--amber-9);
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .hero__stance {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>